---
title: Everything-Bagel Egg Biscuit Sliders 3x the delicious servings!
description: You know those mouthwatering breakfast biscuit sandwiches you’re always craving? (It’s not just us, right?) Get ready to whip up a whole bunch to enjoy for breakfast all week, or to feed a hungry crowd on a lazy Sunday. You’ll cook the eggs in a baking dish with cheddar and zesty scallions to fluffy perfection. Cut them into neat little squares, and serve them on fluffy buttermilk biscuits (let’s hear it for ready-to-bake dough sprinkled with zippy, savory everything bagel seasoning!). Add a dash of hot sauce if you like, then commence the devouring.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/654243d4d4ae2bce30667e31-226ba5a6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/654243d4d4ae2bce30667e31.pdf
